University Press of America, 211&ndash;243.</li>

<li>Fronterotta, F., 2022, &ldquo;Two Remarks on False Opinion between
Epistemology and Ontology in <em>Theaetetus</em>
187b&ndash;201c,&rdquo; in Zucca 2022, 249&ndash;270.</li>

<li>Giannantoni, G., 1958, <em>I Cirenaici: Raccolta delle fonti
antiche, traduzione e studio introduttivo</em>, Florence:
Sansoni.</li>

<li>Giannopoulou, Z., 2013, <em>Plato&rsquo;s</em> Theaetetus <em>as a
Second</em> Apology, Oxford: Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, &ldquo;Socratic Midwifery and Noble
Sophistry: An Intertextual Reading,&rdquo; in Zucca 2022,
163&ndash;176.</li>

<li>Giardina, G.R., 2022, &ldquo;<em>Homoi&ocirc;sis The&ocirc;i</em>
(Plato, <em>Theaetetus</em> 176b1) in Late Neoplatonism,&rdquo; in
Zucca 2022, 325&ndash;352.</li>

<li>Giovannetti, L., 2022, Eidos kai dynamis<em>: The Intertwinement
