<li>Lutoslawski, W., 1905, <em>Origin and Growth of Plato&rsquo;s
Logic</em>, London: Longmans.</li>

<li>Maffi, E., 2013, <em>Lo spazio della filosofia: Una lettura
del</em> Teeteto <em>di Platone</em>, Naples: Loffredo.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2022, &ldquo;The Soul as an Aviary: A
