43&ndash;60.</li>

<li>Moss, J., 2021, <em>Plato&rsquo;s Epistemology: Being and
Seeming</em>, Oxford: Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>Narcy, M. (ed.), 1995, <em>Platon:
Th&eacute;&eacute;t&egrave;te</em>, Paris: Flammarion.</li>

<li>Owen, G.E.L., 1965, &ldquo;The Place of the <em>Timaeus</em> in
