<li>Penner, T., and Rowe, C. (eds.), 2005, <em>Plato&rsquo;s
Lysis.</em> Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Polansky, R.M., 1992, <em>Philosophy and Knowledge: A Commentary
on Plato&rsquo;s</em> Theaetetus, Lewisburg-London-Toronto: Bucknell
